                                                                    <td class="edu" style="padding:8px; font-color: white; text-align: left; border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204);background-color: #2166a1;"> <span style="color:#ffffff;"><b>CURRENT SCENARIO</b></span></td>
                                                                    <td class="edu" style="padding:8px; font-color: white; text-align: left; border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204);background-color: #2166a1;"> <span style="color:#ffffff;"><b>YOU CAN MAKE THE DIFFERENCE</b></span></td>
                                                                </tr>
                                                                <tr>
                                                                    <td class="related-links-td edu"> Parents concern on quality of Government schools</td>
                                                                    <td class="related-links-td edu"> •Modern teaching and learning aids<br> •Sponsor books/periodicals/news papers</td>
                                                                </tr>
                                                                <tr>
                                                                    <td class="related-links-td edu" style="background-color: #dcd9d9;"> Decreased feeling of social ownership in public institutions</td>
                                                                    <td class="related-links-td edu" style="background-color: #dcd9d9;">
                                                                        <p> Ensure participation of parents/old students/social activists/well known<br> personalities of that area in the management of schools</p>
                                                                    </td>
                                                                </tr>
                                                                <tr>
                                                                    <td class="related-links-td edu"> Lack of proper infrastructure and equipments</td>
                                                                    <td class="related-links-td edu"> Provide smart tools for one class room/whole school</td>
                                                                </tr>
                                                                <tr>
                                                                    <td class="related-links-td edu" style="background-color: #dcd9d9;"> Lack of public transportation facilities in rural areas</td>
                                                                    <td class="related-links-td edu" style="background-color: #dcd9d9;"> Sponsor safe transportation facilities bus/van/ferry</td>
                                                                </tr>
                                                                <tr>
                                                                    <td class="related-links-td edu"> Demand for individual attention and care are not fulfilled</td>
                                                                    <td class="related-links-td edu"> Individualized instruction and learning support by expert teachers</td>
                                                                </tr>
